&lt;li&gt;Take pride in software quality through rigorous functional testing and writing automated unit tests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot production issues, provide resolutions and recommendations for improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
